column2: SELECT TOP # sp.fibermag_u-sp.fibermagerr_u as fib_u, sp.fibermag_g-sp.fibermagerr_g as fib_g, sp.fibermag_r-sp.fibermagerr_r as fib_r, sp.fibermag_i-sp.fibermagerr_i as fib_i, sp.fibermag_z-sp.fibermagerr_z as fib_z, sp.fibermag_u-sp.fibermagerr_u-sp.fibermag_g+sp.fibermagerr_g as co1#, sp.fibermag_g-sp.fibermagerr_g-sp.fibermag_r+sp.fibermagerr_r as co1#, sp.fibermag_r-sp.fibermagerr_r-sp.fibermag_i+sp.fibermagerr_i as co1#, sp.fibermag_i-sp.fibermagerr_i-sp.fibermag_z+sp.fibermagerr_z as co1#, sp.petromag_u-sp.petromagerr_u as pet_u, sp.petromag_g-sp.petromagerr_g as pet_g, sp.petromag_r-sp.petromagerr_r as pet_r, sp.petromag_i-sp.petromagerr_i as pet_i, sp.petromag_z-sp.petromagerr_z as pet_z, sp.petromag_u-sp.petromagerr_u -sp.petromag_g+sp.petromagerr_g as co2#, sp.petromag_g-sp.petromagerr_g -sp.petromag_r+sp.petromagerr_r as co2#, sp.petromag_r-sp.petromagerr_r -sp.petromag_i+sp.petromagerr_i as co2#, sp.petromag_i-sp.petromagerr_i -sp.petromag_z+sp.petromagerr_z as co2#, sp.class as class, gx.petroR9#_r/gx.petroR5#_r as mor_#, gx.petroR9#_z/gx.petroR5#_z as mor_#, sp.z as redshift FROM SpecPhoto AS sp   JOIN galaxy AS gx ON sp.specobjid = gx.specobjid  WHERE   sp.z > # and sp.z< #
